        "content": "<p>Does anyone know how to prove the following without having to use  right three times</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">case</span> <span class=\"n\">or.inr</span> <span class=\"n\">or.inr</span>\n<span class=\"n\">PQRS</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span>\n<span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Q</span>\n<span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">⊢</span> <span class=\"n\">P</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span> <span class=\"bp\">∨</span> <span class=\"n\">P</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"bp\">∨</span> <span class=\"n\">Q</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span> <span class=\"bp\">∨</span> <span class=\"n\">Q</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Here is my solution for reference</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">right</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">right</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">right</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">exact</span> <span class=\"o\">⟨</span> <span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">h2</span> <span class=\"o\">⟩</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Thank you</p>",
